Text Captcha for Nette
-----------------------------
1. Copy whole folder TextCapcha into your APP_DIR
2. Extend Form:

	\Nette\Forms\Container::extensionMethod('addTextCaptcha', array('\TextCaptcha\TextCaptcha', 'addTextCaptcha'));

3. Provide session:

	TextCaptcha::setSession(\Nette\Environment::getSession());

4. Provide backend:

	TextCaptcha::setBackend(new ArrayBackend());

5. Set language: 

	TextCaptcha::setLanguage("cs");

6. Add your own questions into dataset - to be on the safe side.



Own backend
------------------------------

1. Must implement interface IBackend.
2. Use efective methods (ORDER BY RAND() is not!)